# ── Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# config.json holds live Pexels / Pixabay / Gemini keys. Never commit it.
# config.example.json is the safe template — that one IS tracked.
config.json

# ── Generated and downloadable ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# All of this rebuilds itself from the sheets. Committing it would push the
# repo into the gigabytes and GitHub rejects any single file over 100 MB.
.venv/
cache/
work/
out/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ── Reference audio ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tracked. These are LibriVox recordings (public domain), they are small, and
# having them travel with the repo means a fresh clone can voice immediately.
# If you ever add a clip you do NOT hold redistribution rights to, add it here
# by name and copy it between machines by hand instead.

# ── Music ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Background tracks are licensed to you, not necessarily redistributable.
music/*
!music/README.txt

# ── OS clutter ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
